headline: ROLLINS, INC. SCHEDULES DATE FOR RELEASE OF THIRD QUARTER 2025 FINANCIAL RESULTS
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, today announced that it will release its third quarter results for the period ended September 30, 2025, after the market closes on Wednesday, October 29, 2025. In conjunction with its release, the Company will host a conference call to review the Company's financial and operating results before the market opens on Thursday, October 30, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Avoid
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
